high_descs: Turn around, go forward to the counter to the right of the sink.
Take the towel hanging to the right of the mirror.
Go to the left to the sink and face the sink.
Put the towel on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn right.
Take the towel hanging to the left of the mirror.
Go to the right to the sink and face the sink.
Put the towel on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put two towels on either side of a sink.

high_descs: Turn around, proceed across from counter.
Remove towel from towel holder on wall.
Turn left, proceed to sink on right.  Turn right to face sink.
Place towel on counter to right of sink.
Turn left to proceed to wall.  Turn right to face counter and towel.
Remove towel from wall.
Turn right, move to sink on left.  Turn left to face sink.
Put towel on counter on left side of sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two towels from wall towel holders to opposite sides of sink.

high_descs: Turn left and take a step forward, then turn left and walk over to the counter.
Take the wash cloth off of the metal right to the right of the mirror.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the counter.
Put the wash cloth on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn left and walk over to the wall, then turn right.
Take the wash cloth off of the metal ring that is on the wall to the left of the mirror.
Turn right and walk towards the shower, then turn left to face the sink.
Put the wash cloth on the counter to the left of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Move two wash cloths to the sink counter.
